[
  {
    "startTime": 18.0,
    "endTime": 21.0,
    "text": "(Heartwarming moments with Disney+ moms and mother figures)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.5,
    "endTime": 24.5,
    "text": "(Pixar's \"Turning Red\")"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.5,
    "endTime": 33.8,
    "text": "Sun Yee, revered ancestor, guardian of the red pandas."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.9,
    "endTime": 38.9,
    "text": "We humbly thank you for protecting and guiding us, especially Mei Mei."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.0,
    "endTime": 42.7,
    "text": "May we continue to serve and honor you and this community."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.2,
    "endTime": 44.300000000000004,
    "text": "- Always.  - Always."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.6,
    "endTime": 55.5,
    "text": "You ready?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.8,
    "endTime": 57.199999999999996,
    "text": "Let's do this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.5,
    "endTime": 60.8,
    "text": "(\"The Wonder Years\")"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.2,
    "endTime": 62.6,
    "text": "I know I didn't deserve to win."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.4,
    "endTime": 66.5,
    "text": "How you treat people comes back around⏤remember that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.2,
    "endTime": 69.3,
    "text": "I'm really sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.4,
    "endTime": 79.9,
    "text": "I figure you want to start practicing for next year."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.0,
    "endTime": 82.0,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.3,
    "endTime": 87.39999999999999,
    "text": "(\"The Mighty Ducks: Game Changers\")"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.5,
    "endTime": 89.3,
    "text": "But, wait, who's going to be your coach?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.7,
    "endTime": 90.7,
    "text": "It's you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.8,
    "endTime": 91.89999999999999,
    "text": "It has to be you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.6,
    "endTime": 95.6,
    "text": "Me? I have never even played hockey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.3,
    "endTime": 97.7,
    "text": "You can do anything, Mom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.2,
    "endTime": 100.2,
    "text": "Come here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.5,
    "endTime": 104.5,
    "text": "(\"Big Hero 6\")"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.8,
    "endTime": 105.89999999999999,
    "text": "Tell me you're OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.0,
    "endTime": 107.2,
    "text": "- We're fine.  - We're OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.3,
    "endTime": 108.3,
    "text": "Oh, good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.7,
    "endTime": 110.7,
    "text": "Then, what were you two knuckleheads thinking?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.0,
    "endTime": 114.9,
    "text": "For 10 years, I have done the best I could to raise you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.6,
    "endTime": 117.1,
    "text": "Have I been perfect? No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.2,
    "endTime": 119.3,
    "text": "Do I know anything about children? No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.3,
    "endTime": 121.1,
    "text": "Should I have picked up a book on parenting?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.2,
    "endTime": 122.2,
    "text": "Probably."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.3,
    "endTime": 123.39999999999999,
    "text": "Where was I going with this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.5,
    "endTime": 124.3,
    "text": "I had a point."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.7,
    "endTime": 125.5,
    "text": "Sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.6,
    "endTime": 126.69999999999999,
    "text": "We love you, Aunt Cass."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.8,
    "endTime": 128.2,
    "text": "Well, I love you, too!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.2,
    "endTime": 132.1,
    "text": "(\"black-ish\")"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.2,
    "endTime": 135.89999999999998,
    "text": "I just wanted to come down here to tell you that I love you,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.3,
    "endTime": 137.9,
    "text": "and I support you,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.4,
    "endTime": 139.9,
    "text": "unconditionally."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.0,
    "endTime": 141.0,
    "text": "Thanks, Mom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.2,
    "endTime": 145.1,
    "text": "(Marvel Studios' \"Avengers: Endgame\")"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.2,
    "endTime": 148.39999999999998,
    "text": "Everyone fails at who they're supposed to be, Thor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.2,
    "endTime": 151.89999999999998,
    "text": "The measure of a person, of a... a hero..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.5,
    "endTime": 155.5,
    "text": "... is how well they succeed at being who they are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.8,
    "endTime": 162.5,
    "text": "I really missed you, Mom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.0,
    "endTime": 168.7,
    "text": "(\"Big Shot\")"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.7,
    "endTime": 170.2,
    "text": "I didn't give birth to you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.4,
    "endTime": 177.6,
    "text": "But from the first moment that I held you,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.8,
    "endTime": 184.70000000000002,
    "text": "I knew that you are my daughter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.0,
    "endTime": 189.0,
    "text": "Baby."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.1,
    "endTime": 196.9,
    "text": "(\"Encanto\")"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.0,
    "endTime": 200.0,
    "text": "I wish you could see yourself the way I do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.5,
    "endTime": 204.2,
    "text": "You are perfect... just like this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.3,
    "endTime": 208.10000000000002,
    "text": "You're just as special as anyone else in this family."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.0,
    "endTime": 213.1,
    "text": "You just healed my hand with an arepa con queso."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.5,
    "endTime": 218.2,
    "text": "I healed your hand with love for my daughter,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.3,
    "endTime": 220.4,
    "text": "with her wonderful brain..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.6,
    "endTime": 223.6,
    "text": "- ... big heart, cool glasses...  - Stop. Mama."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.7,
    "endTime": 227.7,
    "text": "(Thank you to all the mothers, grandmothers, and mother figures who make every day more magical.)"
  }
]